-- Paris prosecution opens SocGen criminal probe
-- 
-- Thu Jan 24, 2008 10:36am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/01/24/us-socgen-investigation-idUSPAB00379120080124

 

 PARIS  (Reuters) - The Paris prosecutor's office said on Thursday it had opened a preliminary criminal investigation into the presumed case of fraud at Societe Generale following a complaint by a shareholder. 

 "The prosecutor's office has seized the financial brigadecomplaint for a preliminary investigation following this compaint," a spokesman for Prosecutor Jean-Claude Marin said. (Reporting by Thierry Leveque; writing by  James Mackenzie  and Francois Murphy)